{
  "texts": [
    "Table 2: Experimental Results for Long Range Image Classification",
    "We now test the performance of recurrent transformers on several datasets.",
    "The goal of our experiments is to test whether smaller single-layer recurrent transformers can match the performance of larger multi-layer transformers at lower computational cost.",
    "Owing to budge constraints, all of our experiments were run on an M4 Mac Mini with 16GB memory.",
    "All of our experiments use positional encoding of tokens and the AdamW optimizer."
  ]
}